      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/22/220",
      "text": [
        " «إِنْ كَانَ أَجْنَبَ هُوَ فَلْيَغْتَسِلْ وَ إِنْ كَانَ اِحْتَلَمَ فَلْيَتَيَمَّمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.220 - It was asked of Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about a man with smallpox who became junub (ritually impure due to sexual discharge).\nImam (as) said: 'If he became junub (through intercourse), he should perform ghusl, but if he had a nocturnal emission (i.e., he experienced it while sleeping), he should perform tayammum.'."
        ]
      }
    },
